{"start": "20260110_130414", "end": "20260110_130414", "time": 0.4066445827484131, "tool_name": "execute_python", "result": {"success": false, "preview": "\"Execution failed with exit code 1\\nNameError: name 'var_functions' is not defined\""}, "args": {"code": "import json\norder_items = var_functions.query_db_11\ncases = var_functions.query_db_5\n\n# Extract order item IDs for the product\norder_item_ids = [item['Id'] for item in order_items]\n\n# Filter cases where orderitemid__c is in our order item list\n# Also handle potential corruption (leading # and trailing whitespace)\nfiltered_cases = []\nfor case in cases:\n    case_orderitem_id = case['orderitemid__c']\n    if case_orderitem_id:\n        # Normalize ID (remove leading # and trailing whitespace)\n        normalized_case_id = case_orderitem_id.lstrip('#').strip()\n        for order_item_id in order_item_ids:\n            normalized_order_item_id = order_item_id.lstrip('#').strip()\n            if normalized_case_id == normalized_order_item_id:\n                filtered_cases.append(case)\n                break\n\n# Count occurrences of each issueid__c\nissue_counts = {}\nfor case in filtered_cases:\n    issue_id = case['issueid__c']\n    if issue_id in issue_counts:\n        issue_counts[issue_id] += 1\n    else:\n        issue_counts[issue_id] = 1\n\n# Find the most frequent issue\nif issue_counts:\n    most_frequent_issue_id = max(issue_counts, key=issue_counts.get)\n    result = most_frequent_issue_id\nelse:\n    result = None\n\n# Print result in the required format\nprint('__RESULT__:')\nprint(json.dumps(result))", "env": {"var_functions.list_db:0": ["Case", "knowledge__kav", "issue__c", "casehistory__c", "emailmessage", "livechattranscript"], "var_functions.query_db:2": [{"id": "#500Wt00000DDDfwIAH", "issueid__c": "a03Wt00000JqzSfIAJ", "orderitemid__c": "802Wt00000797r4IAA", "createddate": "2023-07-02T11:00:00.000+0000"}, {"id": "500Wt00000DDNYoIAP", "issueid__c": "a03Wt00000JqtOtIAJ", "orderitemid